---
---

<section class="relative h-full overflow-hidden">
  {/* Background — halftone grunge, covers ~72% from top. Below is a solid
      dark band that hosts the bio paragraph. */}
  <div
    class="absolute inset-x-0 top-0 h-[72%] bg-cover bg-center"
    style="background-image: url('/joe-bg.webp');"
  >
  </div>
  <div class="absolute inset-x-0 top-[72%] bottom-0 bg-[color:var(--color-bg)]"></div>

  <div class="relative h-full flex flex-col">
    {/* Visual area — logo+button left, portrait right (inline grid keeps it
        responsive; portrait is hidden below md so it can't overlap content). */}
    <div class="flex-1 min-h-0">
      <div
        class="relative h-full max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-10 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[1fr_1fr] items-end md:items-center gap-4 md:gap-8 pt-20 md:pt-24"
      >
        <div class="flex flex-col items-start gap-5 z-10 self-center">
          <img
            src="/joe-logo.png"
            alt="Josef Anolin — Stand-Up Comedian"
            class="w-full max-w-xs sm:max-w-sm md:max-w-md drop-shadow-[0_8px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)]"
          />
          <a
            href="#contact"
            class="inline-block px-10 py-3.5 bg-[color:var(--color-accent)] text-black font-extrabold tracking-widest text-base rounded-full shadow-[0_8px_24px_rgba(193,252,80,0.25)] hover:scale-[1.04] active:scale-[0.97] transition-transform"
          >
            BOOK ME!
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="hidden md:flex justify-end items-end h-full pb-0 md:pb-[-8%]">
          <img
            src="/joe-hero.png"
            alt="Portrait of Josef Anolin"
            class="hero-portrait pointer-events-none select-none w-auto h-auto max-h-[80%] lg:max-h-[88%] object-contain object-bottom"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    {/* Bio band */}
    <div class="relative z-10 px-6 pb-8 pt-5 md:pb-12 md:pt-6 text-center">
      <p
        class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-neutral-200 leading-loose text-sm md:text-base"
      >
        From Oakland, California currently living in Los Angeles, Josef has
        opened for the likes of Tom Segura, Whitney Cummings, and Michael Che.
        He likes telling irreverent stories based on his life and observations.
        He has an Android phone because he likes pissing you off with his green
        text bubbles.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
